Functional Overview
	AvaTax OnDemand is a powerful, online sales tax compliance solution that provides businesses with sales tax automation. 

	During check out shopping cart and customer information is transmitted via Avatax API web service specifications. Tax information is sent back and applied to products in the cart. 

	Advanced Address Validation logic has been added to assist with filtering certain countries (configured in the custom site preferences) and to enable/disable the AVS calls. 

	A testing center hasbeen added to assist clients and developers with testing connections and committing tax requests to the Avatax console. 

	Detailed transaction logging on the Avatax console. 

	A customer code has been added to the Customer object in Business Manager so each customer will have a unique code. 